'''莫吉拉熙笃会修道院''' ({{lang-pl|Opactwo Cystersów w Mogile}}; {{lang-la|Abbatia B.M.V. de Clara Tumba}})<ref>{{cite web|url=http://win.ocist.org/pdf/ELENCHUS_22aprile.pdf|work=Cistercian Order|title=Elenchus Monasteriorum Ordinis Cisterciensis|page=45|access-date=2015-01-26|archive-date=2013-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130627004442/http://win.ocist.org/pdf/ELENCHUS_22aprile.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>位于波兰[[克拉科夫|克拉科夫]]，是一座[[熙笃会|熙笃会]]修道院 。1222年由克拉科夫主教创建<ref name="Mogila Abbey" /><ref name="Jankosz-1">{{cite web | url=http://www.mogila.cystersi.pl/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=151:ogrod-w-mogile&catid=119:ogrod-klasztorny&Itemid=122 | title=Ogród Opactwa Cystersów w Mogile | publisher=Opactwo Cystersów w Mogile | work=Official website | date=15 July 2013 | accessdate=24 July 2013 | author=Krzysztof Jankosz | quote=''Abstract in English:'' [http://www.mogila.cystersi.pl/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=102&Itemid=170  "The Sanctuary Of The Holy Cross Of The Cistercian Abbey In Mogiła."] | archive-date=2019-09-18 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190918023356/http://www.mogila.cystersi.pl/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=151:ogrod-w-mogile&catid=119:ogrod-klasztorny&Itemid=122 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。这是波兰中世纪最大、最重要的教堂之一，仅次于[[克拉科夫圣达尼老圣文策老圣殿总主教座堂|克拉科夫圣达尼老圣文策老圣殿总主教座堂]], and served as the [[House_of_Odrowąż|Odrowąż family's]] burial place until the 16th century.<ref name="Kołodziejczyk-2">{{cite web | url=http://www.mogila.cystersi.pl/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=46:omodlone-wiekami-miejsce&catid=36:historia&Itemid=84 | title=Omodlone wiekami miejsce | publisher=Opactwo Cystersów w Mogile | work=Source: "[[Głos_–_Tygodnik_Nowohucki|Głos – Tygodnik Nowohucki]]", 8 Sep 2000, nr 37 (492), pp. 1 / 9 | date=15 July 2013 | accessdate=24 July 2013 | author=Iwo Kołodziejczyk | language=pl | archive-date=2020-09-18 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200918133403/http://www.mogila.cystersi.pl/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=46:omodlone-wiekami-miejsce&catid=36:historia&Itemid=84 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

该建筑群包括哥特式的圣十字圣殿({{lang-pl|Bazylika Krzyża Świętego}})、修道院教堂，以及文艺复兴风格的院长宫，建于1569年。

